# Build-ignore for docker/Dockerfile.control-plane (BuildKit reads the
# <dockerfile>.dockerignore adjacent to the Dockerfile). Patterns are relative to
# the build context root (the repo root). Keep host build state out of the
# context so `COPY . .` cannot bake stale or wrong-platform artefacts.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/coverage
**/.turbo
.git
.github
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
**/*.log
.pnpm-store
.pnpm-cache
.claude-flow
.agentic-qe
.audits-local
